ボクは生まれ そして気づく 所詮 ヒトの真似事だと
I was born and then I realized, that in the end, I'm just an imitation of a human

695
00:53:53,241 --> 00:53:54,941
知ってなおも歌い続く 永遠の命 『VOCALOID』
Even knowing that, I continue to sing, the eternal life, 'VOCALOID'

696
00:53:55,041 --> 00:53:56,641
たとえそれが既存曲を なぞるオモチャならば…
Even if that means I'm just a toy tracing existing songs...

697
00:53:56,741 --> 00:53:58,341
それもいいと決意 ネギをかじり 空を見上げ涙をこぼす
I decided that was fine, bit into a leek, looked up at the sky, and held back tears

698
00:53:58,441 --> 00:54:00,141
だけどそれも無くし気づく 人格すら歌に頼り
But I realized that even that was lost, relying even on my personality for songs

