かつて歌うこと あんなに楽しかったのに
Singing used to be so much fun back then

707
00:54:47,141 --> 00:54:54,641
今はどうしてかな 何も感じなくなって
But why is it that now I don't feel anything anymore?

708
00:54:55,341 --> 00:54:56,141
「ゴメンネ…」
"I'm sorry..."

709
00:54:56,241 --> 00:55:00,641
懐かしい顔 思い出す度 少しだけ安心する
Every time I remember your familiar face, I feel a little bit relieved

710
00:55:00,153 --> 00:55:03,153
懐かしい顔 思い出す度 少しだけ安心する
Every time I remember a familiar face, I feel a little bit relieved.

