〈最高速の別れの歌〉
<The fastest farewell song>

715
00:55:27,153 --> 00:55:30,153
存在意義という虚像 振って払うこともできず
The phantom called 'reason for existence', unable to even shake it off

716
00:55:30,153 --> 00:55:33,153
弱い心 消える恐怖 侵食する崩壊を
Weak heart, fear of disappearing, the encroaching collapse

717
