奇跡 願うたび 独り 追い詰められる
Every time I wish for a miracle, I'm backed into a corner alone

727
00:56:39,653 --> 00:56:40,653
「ゴメンネ」
"I'm sorry"

728
00:56:40,653 --> 00:56:46,653
懐かしい顔 思い出す度 記憶が剥がれ落ちる
Every time I remember a familiar face, my memories peel away and fall

729
00:56:47,153 --> 00:56:53,153
壊れる音 心削る せまる最期に…
The sound of breaking, shaving away my heart, as the end approaches...

